headline: Incyte (NASDAQ:INCY) Q3 Earnings: Leading The Immuno-Oncology Pack
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at immuno-oncology stocks, starting with Incyte (NASDAQ:INCY).
